## 📦 Installation

### From PyPI (Recommended)

```bash
pip install pydepm
```

### Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/pydepm.git
cd pydepm
pip install -e .
```

### Verify

```bash
python scripts/quick_validation.py
```

